# Deploy after version bump

When you change `SITE_VERSION` in `src/lib/version.ts` (or bump the favicon cache query in `index.html`):

1. Commit all related changes with a clear message.
2. Push to `origin/main` so GitHub Actions deploys to Cloudflare Pages.
3. Confirm the deploy workflow succeeded and share the live URL.

**Do not deploy** only if the user explicitly says not to (e.g. "don't deploy", "hold off on push", "local only").

Manual deploy fallback: `npm run pages:deploy:prod` (requires Cloudflare credentials locally).
